<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٤٦٤ - وَعَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/857">أَيُّوبَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّهُ تَعَشَّى مَرَّةً وَهُوَ يَسْمَعُ قِرَاءَةَ الْإِمَامِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>